ate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="3168:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">user_id</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="3169"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="3169:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">、</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="3170" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="3171"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="3171:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">project_id</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="3172"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="3172:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 这类字段不应该只是普通元数据，而应该成为上下文入口的一部分：它决定这个 Agent 此刻能看见哪个客户、哪个项目、哪一批数据。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-4a81f73b  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="3173"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="3174"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="3174:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以，如果你在做企业级 Agent，不要只检查 prompt 写得好不好，还要检查你的 context schema：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2d9679d5" data-code-language="python" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="3175"><div class="se-67576795 se-525ba532"><span></span></div><div class="se-ac8b18fe se-73f61440"><span></span></div><div class="se-97b8bd37"><div class="se-c096ec1c se-7bcecfca" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-c096ec1c se-7bcecfca" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-c096ec1c se-7bcecfca" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-c096ec1c se-7bcecfca" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-c096ec1c se-7bcecfca" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-c096ec1c se-7bcecfca" data-code-line-number="6"></div></div><div class="se-d8e7900b"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-ob